Comment: I was trying to figure out how to annotate a game, how to save the images, and decided to try one.  Using the keyboard arrow keys moves the pieces on the board.  Wow, just make a comment for a move, click "save, and this is all done automatically!  Photos are automatically saved for any position that you add comments for at the bottom.  This is quite a quality feature.  The annotation didn't show up for awhile, then appeared.
